<th style="background: #ccf; text-align: center; font-size:99%; padding-left:5px; padding-right:5px;">
<div class="noprint plainlinksneverexpand navbar" style="background:none; padding:0; font-weight:normal;; font-size:xx-small; color:;float:left; text-align:left; width:6em;"><a href="/wiki/Template:Books_of_Ketuvim" title="Template:Books of Ketuvim"><span title="View this template" style="">v</span></a>&#160;<span style="font-size:80%;">•</span>&#160;<a href="/w/index.php?title=Template_talk:Books_of_Ketuvim&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Template talk:Books of Ketuvim (page does not exist)"><span title="Discussion about this template" style="">d</span></a>&#160;<span style="font-size:80%;">•</span>&#160;<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Books_of_Ketuvim&amp;action=edit" class="external text" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Books_of_Ketuvim&amp;action=edit" rel="nofollow"><span title="Edit this template" style=";">e</span></a></div>
<span style="font-size:110%;">Books of <a href="/wiki/Ketuvim" title="Ketuvim">Ketuvim</a></span></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style="text-align:left;"><b>Three Poetic Books</b></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="padding-left: 5px;">1. <i><a href="/wiki/Psalms" title="Psalms">Psalms</a></i></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="padding-left: 5px;">2. <i><a href="/wiki/Book_of_Proverbs" title="Book of Proverbs">Proverbs</a></i></td>
