<li id="cite_note-6"><b><a href="#cite_ref-6" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFKelly2006">Kelly, Henry Ansgar (2006). <i><a href="http://www.cambridge.org/catalogue/catalogue.asp?isbn=9780521843393&amp;ss=exc" class="external text" title="http://www.cambridge.org/catalogue/catalogue.asp?isbn=9780521843393&amp;ss=exc" rel="nofollow">Satan:A Biography</a></i>. Cambridge University Press<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.cambridge.org/catalogue/catalogue.asp?isbn=9780521843393&amp;ss=exc" class="external free" title="http://www.cambridge.org/catalogue/catalogue.asp?isbn=9780521843393&amp;ss=exc" rel="nofollow">http://www.cambridge.org/catalogue/catalogue.asp?isbn=9780521843393&amp;ss=exc</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Satan%3AA+Biography&amp;rft.aulast=Kelly&amp;rft.aufirst=Henry+Ansgar&amp;rft.au=Kelly%2C+Henry+Ansgar&amp;rft.date=2006&amp;rft.pub=Cambridge+University+Press&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cambridge.org%2Fcatalogue%2Fcatalogue.asp%3Fisbn%3D9780521843393%26ss%3Dexc&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Book_of_Job"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
